{"tid":2183603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【眨眼變成人】洗米華囡囡18歲","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:38:47.000Z","uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":279,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"816b935891d7b242ccdc01cc097ce482ef9dfee8","tid":2183603,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"太陽娛樂揸弗人周焯華（洗米華）和老婆陳慧玲（Heidi）女兒周梓潼（Virginia）昨日18歲生日，一家人之前已替她舉辦生日會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/58Sw48BXm-JJEJTGYM_Adl6WGvU=/453x551/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/37QXOVLCRRFFZNRWW7YUF2RWVQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F58Sw48BXm-JJEJTGYM_Adl6WGvU%3D%2F453x551%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F37QXOVLCRRFFZNRWW7YUF2RWVQ.JPG&h=c675dd21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洗米女周梓潼終於成人。"},{"pid":"3b95bfeafce91210b1df8370c744f62b99e649b8","tid":2183603,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"洗米嫂Heidi昨晚在IG貼出母女相，並給成年的Virginia深情寄語：「女，你今日正正式式踏入18歲了，回想起當天我自己18歲嘅時候，都好多感慨。不經不覺，你都已經18歲啦，當然好開心你現在可以有你自己嘅閱歷同精彩，祝福你將來的青春無限，豐富人生，但不要忘記感恩，最緊要擁抱自己的未來！愛你！」網民都留言送祝福，「成人了還是要聽媽媽的話」、「感恩之心常在真的好重要！媽媽這番話好正能量」。"},{"pid":"13d4eebb1e4aa913477dbff848b2da3ea343ee26","tid":2183603,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":73,"score":-71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tys86yF_4VHq7XC2I9LB-3-7gXY=/535x550/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYQHKUFFJVGRXAJHORVJZUYYSM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ftys86yF_4VHq7XC2I9LB-3-7gXY%3D%2F535x550%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYQHKUFFJVGRXAJHORVJZUYYSM.JPG&h=323fb13a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n童年時的洗米女。"},{"pi